; ── Phase 3 — Statue of Liberty ───────────────────────────────────────────────
; Boss reaches right and grabs the statue; tentacle weak point wraps the head.
; StatueNode is hidden until Phase 3 (Boss.cs sets Visible=true on phase entry).
; Phase3Controller (Slice 6) drives the swing arc + shuriken fling.
[node name="StatueNode" type="Node2D" parent="."]
